---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy';
const description =
  'Moving Cars is committed to protecting your privacy in your dealings with our organisation. Read our full privacy policy here.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
      >
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-8 text-slate-900 tracking-tight"
        >
          Protecting Your Privacy
        </h1>

        <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
            Moving Cars is committed to protecting your privacy in your dealings
            with our organisation.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            Collection of Information
          </h2>
          <p>
            ‘Personal Information’ is defined in the Privacy Act 1988 as
            Information or an opinion (including information or an opinion
            forming part of a database), whether true or not and whether
            recorded in a material form or not, about an individual whose
            identity is apparent or can reasonably be ascertained from the
            information or opinion.
          </p>
          <p>
            The collection of personal information is necessary for the general
            operation of our business, or to provide you with the products
            and/or services we provide.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            Disclosure
          </h2>
          <p>
            Moving Cars will not provide any personal information collected, to
            any persons outside of Moving Cars, other than to provide the
            services or products that you requested, or other than for
            employment, or legal, or lawful purposes. This may (but is not
            limited to) include disclosing information to Legal/Law Enforcement
            Agencies/Agents, and Government agencies such as (but not limited
            to) the Australian Taxation Office, WorkCover, Department of Social
            Services, and Child Support Agencies.
          </p>
          <p>
            Other than stated above, Moving Cars will not disclose personal
            information, unless you have authorised us to do so.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            Access and Correction of Personal Data
          </h2>
          <p>
            If at any time the personal information you have supplied to Moving
            Cars needs to be accessed by yourself or altered in any way, this
            will be provided only to the person/s named on such information and
            only by written application accompanying suitable identification.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Security</h2>
          <p>
            Whilst Moving Cars takes reasonable steps to protect your personal
            information, sending and receiving information over the Internet is
            always at your own risk. No guarantee can be given that information
            sent over the Internet is completely secure.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">
            Credit Card Details
          </h2>
          <p>
            Any transactions using credit cards via our website are processed by
            the ANZ eGate system. We do not store credit card details processed
            online.
          </p>

          <div
            class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 p-6 my-8 rounded-r-xl"
          >
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-0">
              Please note we do not under any circumstances sell or trade your
              email address or any other contact details.
            </p>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Should you have any questions or complaints about privacy issues
            please contact <span class="font-bold">Moving Cars</span>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote CTA -->
        <div
          class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl mt-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8"
        >
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Ready to move your car?</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">
              Get an instant, obligation-free quote today.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/quote/"
            class="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-slate-900 font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-xl transition-all transform hover:scale-105 inline-block text-center whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            Get Instant Quote
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
